OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FThe government-ordered National
OL,7,FMaternity and Neonatal Investigation
OL,8,Ffound a system that is still not
OL,9,Fworking for women, babies or staff, as
OL,10,FITV News Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,11,FBarry reports
OL,13,FNHS maternity services are failing
OL,14,Fwomen, through a raft of problems
OL,15,Franging from a reluctance to admit
OL,16,Fmistakes, racism, staff shortages, and
OL,17,F"a lack of kindness and compassion,"
OL,18,Faccording to a government-ordered
OL,19,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
