OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772193828
OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FAn interim report published by
OL,7,FBaroness Amos as part of her National
OL,8,FMaternity and Neonatal Investigation
OL,9,Ffound deep-rooted issues across the
OL,10,FNHS and a system that "is not working
OL,11,Ffor women, babies and families, or for
OL,12,Fstaff".
OL,14,FStories her team heard included a
OL,15,Fdelivery where the delivery room was
OL,16,Ftoo small so a "door had to be left
OL,17,Fopen to provide enough space ` with a
OL,18,Fscreen placed outside of the room to
OL,19,Fprotect families' privacy."
OL,26,@rD@WOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772193828
OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FIt added: "It is inconceivable that
OL,7,Fanyone would choose to give birth in
OL,8,Fsuch a manner. We have to ask
OL,9,Fourselves how this can be regarded as
OL,10,Facceptable in 2026?"
OL,12,FRacism was also often reported to
OL,13,Finvestigators, including black woman
OL,14,Fsaying they had been told they had
OL,15,F"'tough skin' and able to tolerate
OL,16,Fpain."
OL,18,FThe team also heard that families were
OL,19,Foften not given information about
OL,20,Fwhether their baby had been born alive.
OL,26,@rD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
